#. [message]: speaker=$ally_name
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/utils/deaths.cfg:149
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/utils/deaths.cfg:174
msgid "No, $unit.name can't die now!"
